title: Youtube video sounds crackling and popping
content:
Im on the latest version of Mac OS and Firefox and it seems to be a recurring issue.

when playing Youtube videos. sounds keep crackling or popping here and there. it is only on Youtube videos. when I run normal videos through quicktime player, iina, etc.. there's no problem

its only youtube.
